docs.snippet: Yes, there are futuristic mega malls and skyscrapers. But you’ll also find a rich cultural heritage reflected in traditional temples and shrines, street food and homegrown art.
In the hit movie “Crazy Rich Asians,” the country looks luxe. But it’s easy to have a great time (and eat memorably well) without spending much.

headline.main: Singapore, for Those Who Aren’t Crazy Rich
headline.print_headline: Singapore, if You’re Not Crazy Rich
